data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after, Nassau Crossing! No need to wait for new construction, this home is move-in ready! As you enter, you'll notice the thoughtfully designed split bedroom layout. With 3 beds/2 baths, this home offers ample space for the whole family. The master, located at the back of the home, offers tray ceiling, large walk-in closet, and his/her bathroom vanity. Kitchen boasting granite countertops, white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, large island, and walk-in pantry. NO CDD fees and very low HOA fees! Located near the new William Burgess Park, which includes a playground, trails, fitness stations, dog park and splash pad *coming soon*. Close to hospitals, airport, shopping, Kings Bay Base, and Amelia Island beaches. Home is zoned for the top-rated Yulee School District. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning your life in this wonderful community!
